    "---\n",
    "## Step 5: Summary — What Can We Claim?\n",
    "\n",
    "### Confounding Analysis (Phase B2, n=10)\n",
    "\n",
    "| Relationship | r | p | Significant? |\n",
    "|---|---|---|---|\n",
    "| J_topo → loss | " + f\"{r_JL:+.3f}\" + " | " + f\"{p_JL:.4f}\" + " | " + (\"YES\" if p_JL < 0.05 else \"NO\") + " |\n",
    "| Width → loss | " + f\"{r_WL:+.3f}\" + " | " + f\"{p_WL:.4f}\" + " | " + (\"YES\" if p_WL < 0.05 else \"NO\") + " |\n",
    "| J_topo → loss | Width | " + f\"{r_JL_W:+.3f}\" + " | " + f\"{p_JL_W:.4f}\" + " | " + (\"YES\" if p_JL_W < 0.05 else \"NO\") + " |\n",
    "\n",
